EH-024 Why do you keep rejecting my ads?

I'm sorry to hear that your ads are being rejected. Ad rejection reasons can vary, such as incorrect conversion tracking setup for a tCPA campaign or typographical errors. Ad Support will inform you of the specific reasons via email. I recommend checking out our advertising policy before submitting new ads to avoid future rejections. You can find more details here: [My ad got rejected. What's next?](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/18085960681101-My-ad-got-rejected-What-s-next).
